==English==
===Etymology===
From ''un-'' + ''scramble''

===Transitive verb===
'''unscramble'''
#reverse the process of [[scramble|scrambling]] (eggs)
#put into order or restore to order
#render [[intelligible]]
#separate into [[constituent]] parts
#interpret a [[scramble|scrambled]] message

===Derived terms===
*[[unscrambler]]

